items.title: Tribe quickly answers rare deficit with Bruce HR
items.summary: For only the second time in their past 21 games, the Indians did not score first in a ballgame. That rare deficit did not last long, though, as the Tribe took the lead right back in the bottom of the first inning in Wednesday's series finale against the Tigers at Progressive Field.

items.title: Hannah Jeter: Virgin Islands need Irma relief
items.summary: Although her current hometown of Tampa was mostly spared by Hurricane Irma, Hannah Jeter -- the model and wife of Yankees legend Derek Jeter -- took to social media Tuesday to solicit help for her native St. Thomas and the rest of the U.S. Virgin Islands.
